01:11:24.560 --> 01:11:26.160
Ayan tuloy, pare!

01:11:30.880 --> 01:11:31.880
Huwag kang mag-alala.

01:11:32.660 --> 01:11:34.060
Tutulungan kita.

01:11:35.300 --> 01:11:36.600
I swear,

01:11:36.640 --> 01:11:39.040
